com.github.wuic.path.core

Class VirtualDirectoryPath

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.wuic.path.core.VirtualDirectoryPath
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DirectoryPath, Path

    public class VirtualDirectoryPath
extends Object
implements DirectoryPath

    This virtual DirectoryPath is based on a several other DirectoryPath and proxy method call to them when getChild(String) list(), getLastUpdate() are called.

    Note that since there are multiple parent, a UnsupportedOperationException will be thrown is getAbsolutePath() and getParent() are called.

    Since:
    0.5.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
